Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在看昨天那個孩子的戰鬥記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼來歷？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特遇見的那個會駕駛高達的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小的孩子駕駛高達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 德西爾做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛高達幹掉了UE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼輕而易舉地…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我強得多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的船票我替你拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船票？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的新家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往托爾迪亞的定期船票
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5天後就出發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算去托爾迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經數百年宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭終於偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的不明敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天回不了家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是放心 會買禮物回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！ 爸爸最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 真是個現實的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克 不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星安琪兒被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家就在那上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了的話 去艦長室休息如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值班員會繼續進行UE的警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲部分改良成雙層了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被直接命中 就沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫 去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 得到許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故地重遊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故地？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙裏有那種地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不去托爾迪亞？菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在天神號上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想正式申請加入聯邦軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的這麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉和迪克去托爾迪亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特沒有上戰場的義務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你因為伯母的事 恨透了UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是… 不因為那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能成不了救世主那麼厲害的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無法放過那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用高達幫助大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼擅自決定！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 麥德納大叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這不是沃爾夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 蠻精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 上次的機體用膩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了刺激我靈感的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 沃爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的機體？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片是哪兒來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士製造師都認識它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和傳說中的機體一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長著這張臉的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接二連三取得過赫赫戰功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字也跟傳說中一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 在哪看到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過不多久你們也會看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在先替我做份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的是超越高達的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老規矩 要白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪兒去了 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為UE禁止外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉可能去的地方有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏幹什麼 規定不許外出的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回港口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不理解人家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在城裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市裏戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護牆在保護城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人是UE嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼和UE以外的機動戰士隊打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找地方躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎 讓我們進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找得到入口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉·阿蒙德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克·布萊亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是衛星的地下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是衛星內壁和外壁之間的狹縫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裏生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有這麼大的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能住在上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不用為錢煩惱的富裕者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除那以外的人只好住在下面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說 我們這裏是法丁的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰影…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 找到這麼多廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概可以換明天的晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小的孩子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的多虧你出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種地方磨磨蹭蹭地會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從哪來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來自一個叫諾拉的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是外面來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼來法丁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉被UE毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…真是災難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉是什麼地方 有遊樂場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞 爸爸在談重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞到那邊房間去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞 莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是閒不住的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拾到的棄嬰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她當作女兒撫養長大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的戰鬥經常發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 衛星國家戰爭的芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星國家戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指以前地球圈戰爭的遺患嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們出生前好幾代開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中就飄浮著眾多衛星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量增加的衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成扎拉姆聯合和艾烏巴同盟兩大勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生過大規模戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過數十年時間 戰爭結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 付出了太多的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類為了不再重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定把機動戰士等所有戰鬥機器銷毀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 銀杯條約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該就此為宇宙帶來和平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼還有剛才的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流淌在人們血脈中的記憶孕育出仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使戰爭無法結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊國家間的矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍舊存在於這顆衛星上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層的人 過著富裕的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為無聊的思想 沒日沒夜的打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們拜其所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫過著這樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找社長多恩·沃伊諾基
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅汀·蘭布裏克社的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃裏克·斯坦納先生對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃裏克·斯坦納…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此行來做一筆交易
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦軍 天神號戰艦艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍士官來此有何貴幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道你在這座衛星上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從事機動戰士和戰艦的買賣交易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 我完全聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事 請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要四艘戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話說得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的東西就是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報酬是 軍隊的武器數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EZ7號文件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的機密情報！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要賣這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀杯條約以來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵器的情報被全部銷毀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們在高價販賣兵器設計圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再普通不過的一筆交易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪兒找了你這麼個艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不著你們說我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以舊國家之名引發無意義的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中飽私囊的吃貨們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！ 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨換個地方說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去安排車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宅邸招待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意 家常便飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 提速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞 莉莉亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裏了 莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跑到上面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是上面在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方有機動戰士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一起去的話就快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能…能坐得下？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好擠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞 在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼 明明有其他敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 就是因為他們這座衛星才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙 今天絕不放過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生 太蠻幹了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機動戰士不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥又要讓人傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在阿爾塔格達區遭遇MS戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星裏動用高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後會說明情況的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對饒不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生 這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 還沒到？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們愚蠢的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生 聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你 在駕駛那台機動戰士？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生 請退開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機動戰士不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為搞到這台傢伙 我花了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是工業用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機動戰士已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下來 到安全的地方避難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人怎麼能留下小孩自己逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分大人小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下來 不論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓莉莉亞再成為孤兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對莉莉亞來說 你是無可替代的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多茲步槍會殃及城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 只是個普通的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民區發生戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是法丁的內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆和艾烏巴的衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有這麼愚蠢的衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼高達會在那裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧 你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊UE的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此需要戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是UE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是新型的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會出現在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼喜歡嗎 觀看戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只躲沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個距離的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋開了光束？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣打下去的話 城市就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身戰的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器的話威力太大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用高達進行格鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及解析！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞我們城市的不明機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經被完全包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實就範
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 剛才有UE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戰鬥的話 會造成更大的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被扎拉姆抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護了城市！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆和艾烏巴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩大意志孕育出無益的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此時 高達獲得了新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進化的高達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 有一場衛星國家戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星之間分成幾大勢力相互爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中較大的兩個勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆和艾烏巴在戰爭結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.89,0:24:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍舊保留派閥 爭鬥不休

